                        <interp inst="t18620922-name-196" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL TOBIT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman, R</hi> 211). The prisoner was given into my custody—I told her what the charge was, and she said she picked the purse up—at the station she gave this bottle up, and said he had it given her—I asked the prosecutor if that was his; he said "Yes," and that the woman most have taken that too.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">JURY</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> What state was the prosecutor in? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> He was in a state of intoxication, but the other man was not—the prosecutor said there was 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. and some halfpence in the purse—that was before I showed it to him.</p>
